{"tid":656233,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉湖3房逼近600萬，不足4年升近7成","createTime":"2018-05-07T05:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T09:49:11.000Z","uid":73092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c62f3a2f593109b5bb2fb55b5d231a66711a5858","tid":656233,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:07:55.000Z","msg":"天水圍嘉湖山莊剛錄複式破紀錄成交後，屋苑再錄3房成交個案。<br />\n<br />\n中原副區域營業經理伍耀祖表示，屯門新盤御半山近日認購反應熱烈，雖搶去市場焦點，但嘉湖山莊樓價仍較相宜，吸引買家追低水，最新成交位於嘉湖山莊景湖居12座高層D室，實用面積544方呎（建築面積709方呎），3房間隔，以591.8萬元沽出，實呎10879元。<br />\n<br />\n原業主2014年7月以356萬元購入單位，持貨不足4年，帳面獲利235.8萬元，升值66%。"},{"pid":"de3f6dd039d99f64f74e199db6983a3cb97749a8","tid":656233,"uid":5267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad4daa625d563ecb8e2ba4c0c5540815ae78850d","tid":656233,"uid":48235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8012d40e9afb6169cae43bafe04304b85a01859f","tid":656233,"uid":73092,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"ad4daa625d563ecb8e2ba4c0c5540815ae78850d","tid":656233,"uid":48235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20160721/392pix/1469033392_9153.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20160721%2F392pix%2F1469033392_9153.jpg&h=1c120d05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"096eada35d1cd57efb987aa14e3a4dc11a364ecf","tid":656233,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8012d40e9afb6169cae43bafe04304b85a01859f","tid":656233,"uid":73092,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quot